ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">현재 코드 구조와 Supabase 설정을 파악했어요. 회원가입 기능을 추가하는 방법을 설명드릴게요.</p>
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">현재 구조 파악</h2>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">로그인: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">users</code> 테이블에서 <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">phone</code> + <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">user_id</code>로 조회</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">회원 데이터: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">users</code> 테이블 (user_id, name, phone, user_type, cert_level 등)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Supabase Auth를 <strong>사용하지 않고</strong> 직접 DB 조회 방식</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">회원가입 구현 방향</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Supabase Auth를 도입하거나, 현재처럼 <strong>직접 DB 삽입</strong> 방식을 유지하는 두 가지 선택지가 있어요.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">현재 방식(직접 DB)을 유지하는 게 변경이 최소화되므로 그 방향으로 설명할게요.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">1. HTML에 회원가입 화면 추가</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">로그인 화면 아래에 버튼 추가 후, 새 screen 추가:</p>
