<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">2. 아이디 조건</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">현재 코드에 설정된 조건은 이거예요:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>4자 이상</strong> (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">userId.length &lt; 4</code>)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>영문/숫자/언더바만</strong> (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">/^[a-zA-Z0-9_]+$/</code>)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>중복 불가</strong> (DB에서 중복 확인)</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">한글, 공백, 특수문자(@, -, ! 등)는 불가해요.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">기존 회원들 아이디 보면 <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">konu</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">dodo</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">han0601</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">jinwj1996</code> 이런 형태예요.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">조건 바꾸고 싶은 게 있으면 말씀해주세요!</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
