ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">아이폰과 안드로이드 둘 다 적어드릴게요!</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">📱 아이폰 (Safari)</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Safari로 링크 열기</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">하단 <strong>공유 버튼</strong> (□↑) 탭</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>"홈 화면에 추가"</strong> 탭</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">이름 확인 후 <strong>추가</strong> 탭</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">🤖 안드로이드 (Chrome)</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Chrome으로 링크 열기</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">우측 상단 <strong>⋮ 메뉴</strong> 탭</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>"홈 화면에 추가"</strong> 탭</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>추가</strong> 탭</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
