ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">메뉴에 설치 옵션이 안 보이네요. 주소창 오른쪽 끝을 봐주세요 - <strong>다운로드 아이콘(⬇️) 옆에 모니터+화살표 아이콘</strong>이 있을 수 있어요.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">없으면 <strong>Ctrl+Shift+J</strong> 눌러서 콘솔 열고 오류 메시지 있는지 확인해볼게요. manifest.json을 못 찾고 있을 수도 있어요.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
