<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>가장 쉬운 방법:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">아이콘 <strong>우클릭 → 이미지 다른 이름으로 저장</strong> → <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">icon.png</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">GitHub에서 <strong>+ → Upload files</strong> → <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">icon.png</code> 업로드</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">혹시 SVG로 저장되면 <a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://svgtopng.com/">svgtopng.com</a> 에서 PNG 변환 후 올려주세요!</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
